battery on the charger all afternoon. Unfortunately that didn't do it.
With my tail between my legs I went and reinstalled my points. Timing
is jumpy again, which is one of the reason I wanted to go electronic,
I noticed the Hot Spark unit really smoothed that out a lot. If its
not a ground issue I'd figure I'm losing voltage somewhere on the
